raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"lecture_hall\")
Nina: Yo is this Maple's Boytoy?
Player: Yeah?
Player: Who's this?
Nina: Don't fuck with me
Nina: You know who I am
Nina: Think I wouldn't notice you creeping on my Socials huh?
Nina: Maple's been saying you've been mentioning me
Player: Maple?
Player: You mean Mabel?
Nina: I don't give a damn how you spell it
Nina: So what are you, some kinda stalker weirdo?
Player: Was just curious who my girlfriend's been hanging out with
Nina: Yeah, not with YOU
Nina: That's all you should know
Nina: Look, I'll cut to the chase
Nina: I'm bringing Mabel in to the sorority
Nina: She's made for it
Nina: Girl like her were literally made to get fucked and have no place with you
Nina: Don't take it personally
Nina: Actually, take it personally. I couldn't give less of a shit! 🖕
- Wow, you're pleasant
	Player: Wow, you're pleasant
	Nina: I'm only this pleasant to uglies and weirdos who date out their league
	Nina: Maple needs someone better than you
	Nina: Bitch like you is holding her back from her potential
	Nina: Trust me, I've seen it all before
	Nina: But don't break up with her yet
	Nina: I want to watch you squirm all alone when she's thrusting her hips all psychotically 🤤
	Nina: THAT'S ALL YOU'LL GET FROM ME HAHAHA
- Why are you telling me all this?
	Player: Why are you telling me all this?
	Nina: Well duh
	Nina: It messes with your head, don't it?
	- Doesn't bother me at all
		Player: Doesn't bother me at all
		Nina: You're lying
		- Why would I be?
			Player: Why would I be?
			Nina: Don't play tough guy now
			Nina: I know a bluff when I see it
			Nina: THAT'S ALL YOU'LL GET FROM ME HAHAHA
		- You texted me first [#blackheart]
			set Story.black_heart += 1
			Player: You texted me first
			Player: If you were lonely, just say so
			Nina: Why you little shit
			Nina: You really think you're somebody, eh?
			Nina: Won't be the last time you hear from me
			Player: Yeah, I'm sure you'll get lonely again
			Player: I'll be waiting
			Nina: FUCK YOU
			Nina: img: nina/8
			do social_post(\"ninas_rage\")
	- Why would I admit that to you?
		Player: Why would I admit that to you?
		Nina: You don't need to admit it
		Nina: But now I know it's true hah
		Nina: Knew you were a loser
		Nina: THAT'S ALL YOU'LL GET FROM ME HAHAHA
=> END"
